product.title: ANGELA & WILLIAM USA American Flag Straw Cowboy Hat w/Shapeable Brim, Red, White, Navy Blue
product.description: Stylish straw cowboy hat with navy blue background, white stars & red with white stripes. Features coated & formed straw construction that retains its shape for the perfect look. Classic design has a pinch front crown and 3 inch wide shapeable brim. Shape edges to your favorite look. Interior has elastic sweatband for an easy snug fit. One size fits all up to 23 inches. Makes a great gift.
